data.description: Homesite 4 is a basement home on a private, wooded lot. Master suites on both the main and second level. The family room includes a custom fireplace. The gourmet kitchen features a large island and stainless steel appliances. This home is a new start and still has plenty of design selections to be made. Everleigh is a rare find in a top East Cobb location, combining premier, well-designed single-family homes with an excellent school district. Nestled in a wooded enclave, this intimate community features thoughtfully designed floorplans and access to natural green amenities. With a private trail winding through the community, Everleigh is a place all its own, in close proximity to all of East Cobb's top destinations.
